snippet.title: Taiko no Tatsujin: Nijiiro Version - Gameplay 02 (TeknoParrot)
snippet.description:
My Specs |
Windows 11 Pro 64-Bit | 22H2 |
Intel (R) Core (TM) i7-3770S CPU @ 3.10 GHz |
NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1660 6G |
18G RAM |
----------------
Devices Used:
- PC
- Xbox One Controller (Powered A)
Programs Used: 
- OBS Studio (64bit) 
- TeknoParrot 1.0.0.1080 
----------------
Windows Settings
01. Add "Game.exe" to Nvidia Control Panel
02. Turn Off V-sync after adding the game to Nvidia Control Panel
03. Apply Settings.
04. Add Game Folder to Antivirus as Exception to avoid file removal
----------------
TeknoParrot Settings
01. Open TeknoParrot UI Add Game
02. In TeknoParrot UI after adding Game go to "Game Settings" see settings in Picture https://ibb.co/M6Ggs3R
03. Save
04. In TeknoParrot UI Go to "Controller Setup" Configure Controlls, Save
05. "Launch Game" from TeknoParrot UI & Enjoy!
----------------
00:40 - Angel Dream | エンジェルドリーム
04:54 - Tower of Druaga Medley |ドルアーガの塔メドレー
08:29 - Otome Kaibou (乙女解剖) | DECO*27 feat. Hatsune Miku
11:57 - Sacrifice | サクリファイス
15:03 - LOSER | Kenshi Yonezu
17:47 - Zero | 零 -ZERO-
21:50 - Robot Rocking Ro☆ | ロボットロケンロー☆
24:41 - Hyakki Yakou | 百鬼夜行
28:32 - Dokidoki Munekyun Omatsuri Time | ドキドキ胸きゅん おまつりタイム
32:17 - B.B.K.K.B.K.K. | nora2r
----------------
Taiko no Tatsujin (Playlist)
https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLT4MuIIsGR_q_vKbZtU_4Q7RM1VbrXrhZ&si=a8atm5S7NtI5y06Z
----------------
TeknoParrot - Nvidia GPU Tested (Playlist)
https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLT4MuIIsGR_oTG97QNSbm2Us7OJtIck9x&si=D3gYus5Qm888cgJI
----------------
